{"id": 414, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最受不了的电视情节是什么？", "description": "每次看电视的时候，我总是会怀疑自己的智商已超过200。", "record_count": 20155, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606061450566RnfdvuzWb7gYTla.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-06T12:17:40Z", "options": [{"id": 3175, "content": "说最后一次必死", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3182, "content": "各种不必要的矫情误会。白莲花矫情爱哭圣母型女主和面无表情硬装情深智商为零型男主最讨厌了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3180, "content": "800里开外一枪干掉鬼子的机枪手，还有比这个更神的？不服来战", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128795}, {"id": 3329, "content": "受伤的总是男二女二", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234834dY3BGDgQmNwv46VP.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138933}, {"id": 3253, "content": "坏人永远一打就死，好人永远打不死", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138356}, {"id": 3256, "content": "誰是壞人誰是好人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137194}, {"id": 3261, "content": "无论多穷都会在大城市有个装修精美的房子和每天一套的名牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138427}, {"id": 3265, "content": "男一永远能听到女一和其他男的说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138429}, {"id": 3123, "content": "“女强人”角色总是一副六亲不认、唯我独尊的死样，一脸“老娘要跟你拼了”的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131042}, {"id": 3124, "content": "当女主和男主在一起后，各种是是非非，又被拆散，又和好，结局总是完美的。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137047}, {"id": 3126, "content": "“就算全世界的男/女人都死光了，我也不会嫁/娶你。”这样一说出口观众就知道“哦，他们最后在一起了啊”这样的设定…", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137111}, {"id": 3128, "content": "皇帝自称 我", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137130}, {"id": 3129, "content": "一个穷的要死的女主，一个富的只剩钱的男主。然后他们相爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 3131, "content": "男女主会以各种理由同居。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137151}, {"id": 3127, "content": "关键时刻好人出现，你懂的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133628}, {"id": 4121, "content": "车祸必失忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143910}, {"id": 3874, "content": "为了救一个孩纸，死了一大堆队友，最后还要说取得了胜利！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138802}, {"id": 4319, "content": "这个鱼塘被你承包了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135483}, {"id": 3063, "content": "明明车祸时翻白眼，唾沫星子满天飞，脸扭曲的镜头，却可以拍得唯美得不能再唯美！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136531}, {"id": 3064, "content": "?莫过于抗日战争片儿的剧情，奇侠以及手榴弹放在一个很难想象的地方……", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211135tr0VecXTjZCFNWbU.jpg", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98842}, {"id": 3065, "content": "男主的脸盲", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123244}, {"id": 3066, "content": "逃跑必崴脚，还要挥手说“你们快跑～，别管我”", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136563}, {"id": 3068, "content": "点的我手疼，没有一键点赞的功能伐开心:-(", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136560}, {"id": 3067, "content": "作作感情戏，还不分场合的起音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42270}, {"id": 3071, "content": "男女主演了大半部电视剧，好不容易在一起，要不是冒出来个暖心男二或贱贱的女二，要不就是男主或女主失忆谁都没忘记，就忘记那个最重要的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 3069, "content": "把鬼片拍成色情片", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 3070, "content": "女主在摔倒，没钱被房东赶出家门时，总有一个又帅又有钱的男主出来帮他", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 2985, "content": "男女发生误会后，总有在一条街但总是错过的镜头", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200746uGUKNQp2jDgV9oXe.jpg", "praise_count": 269, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 2986, "content": "高富帅总喜欢女屌丝，男屌丝总能勾搭上白富美，还能没理由的爱的死去活来", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004853HlkiR615DpJT9wLP.gif", "praise_count": 430, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 2987, "content": "明明知道是误会，就是不解释。", "image": null, "praise_count": 601, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136166}, {"id": 2988, "content": "上交给国家！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120536}, {"id": 2989, "content": "滚娘的选角", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 2990, "content": "全赞了一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 422, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 2993, "content": "任何死亡场面都太尼玛不真实了。交代遗言的不真实*100", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 2994, "content": "一对相爱的男女，总有一个爱女主的男二", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211136qIGfE1K8T9hzoYXb.jpg", "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 2991, "content": "选项太多，不点?", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130792}, {"id": 3073, "content": "旁白。又是旁白。编剧是不会写台词吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103970}, {"id": 3016, "content": "上交给国家", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136278}, {"id": 3020, "content": "每次都有十分着急/紧要的事要去做，可主角还在那不紧不慢的对台词，让人家观众看得干着急", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132349}, {"id": 3025, "content": "日剧跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133773}, {"id": 3050, "content": "龙套随便哪里中一枪甚至中了一拳两脚就扑街了，主角就算要害中了一枪也能蹦达好久", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3051, "content": "演技太烂，整个片子都没心情看了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136077}, {"id": 3052, "content": "一哭一笑，一笑几哭，加几电灯泡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136445}, {"id": 2955, "content": "男女主必然绝症（幼小的我第一次知道了癌症白血病）", "image": null, "praise_count": 290, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2956, "content": "女扮男装那么明显却永远看不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2957, "content": "男女主永远不能好好说话，一个小误会就是三十集", "image": null, "praise_count": 1431, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2965, "content": "车祸等事故频发", "image": null, "praise_count": 526, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122268}, {"id": 2967, "content": "说书面语", "image": null, "praise_count": 210, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 2962, "content": "男女主永远在彼此需要的时候擦肩而过", "image": null, "praise_count": 900, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101524}, {"id": 2963, "content": "每次女主晕倒必有男生抱住，然后，旋转。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 837, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134053}]}